response.original_title: The People We Hate at the Wedding
response.overview: A dysfunctional family that can't seem to get along and get it together reluctantly reunites for a family wedding. As their many skeletons are wrenched from the closet, it turns out to be just what this singular family needs to reconnect.
response.title: The People We Hate at the Wedding
